<html>
  <style>
    body {
      font: 400 14px/20px Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
    }

    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .support-info {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
    }

    .company-info {
      margin: 0 0 6px 0;
    }

    .policy-links {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
    }

    .support-link {
      color: #0066cc;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .support-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .automated-message {
      margin: 0;
      font-style: italic;
    }
  </style>

  <body>
    <div>
      <img
        src="https://ci3.googleusercontent.com/meips/ADKq_NaCfAJtzjP-oa45zd7M1j5FwbA5QBphzgF9284rBdhyxr1oq8H81MYf-v0m1xHk1N536PIRWDkTI4HVLQwTfViXcORVmWWKKKjcVG6LU0aitT99lOjXph1ovuRV8bE=s0-d-e1-ft#https://staging.bissafety.app/images/EmailNotif_Icon_Completion55x55.png"
        width="30"
      />
      <br />
      <h1 style="color: rgb(64, 68, 113);">Manual Participant ID Verification</h1>
      <span style="color: gray;">{{date}}</span>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p>Hello,</p>
      <p>
        The virtual proctor could not verify the identity of
        <strong>{{participant_name}}</strong> with the government-issued photo ID
        they provided.
      </p>

      <p>
        They continued to take the online course <strong>{{course_name}}</strong>
        on <strong>{{date}}</strong>.
      </p>

      <p>
        Please verify the participant’s identity immediately. Their course
        status will remain pending until your manual verification is complete.
      </p>

      <p>
        <a
          href="{{Link}}"
          target="_blank"
          style="
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #90ee90;
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #5cb85c;
            font-family: sans-serif;
          "
          >Retake</a
        >
      </p>

      <p>Thanks kindly,<br />BIS Safety Software</p>
    </div>

    <div class="email-footer">
      <p class="support-info">
        If you have any questions or believe you received this email in error,
        please contact our Support Team by phone at <strong>1-866-416-1660</strong>
        or by email at
        <a href="mailto:{{supportMail}}" class="support-link"
          >{{supportMail}}</a
        >.
      </p>

      <p class="company-info">
        BIS Safety Software | 261 Seneca Road, Sherwood Park AB T8A 4G6, Canada
      </p>

      <p class="policy-links">
        <a href="{{termsUrl}}" class="support-link">Terms and Conditions</a> |
        <a href="{{privacyUrl}}" class="support-link">Privacy Policy</a>
      </p>

      <p class="automated-message">
        This is an automated email message. Please do not reply to this email
        address.
      </p>
    </div>
    <!-- ============================================================== -->
  </body>
</html>
